    <briefdescription>
<para>Synchronous publish/subscribe event broker. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides a decoupled event system. Modules can subscribe to specific topics and receive callbacks when events are published.</para>
<para>Uses a static caller-provided array for storing subscriptions (zero allocation). </para>
    </detaileddescription>
